## Quick Migration Script

Create `scripts/update-fonts.sh`:

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# Quick find-replace for font updates

# Update h1 tags
find src -name "*.astro" -type f -exec sed -i '' 's/text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold/text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-bold/g' {} +

# Update h2 tags
find src -name "*.astro" -type f -exec sed -i '' 's/text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900/text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-950/g' {} +

# Update large text
find src -name "*.astro" -type f -exec sed -i '' 's/text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900/text-2xl font-display font-bold text-slate-950/g' {} +

echo "Font classes updated! Now manually update:"
echo "1. tailwind.config.mjs"
echo "2. BaseLayout.astro (fonts link)"
echo "3. global.css (font features)"
```

